image_analysis.description: A financial disclosure form, specifically an OGE Form 278e, detailing ownership stakes in various business entities. The document is filled out for Donald J. Trump and lists several entities with reference numbers, ownership percentages, and the names of the owners and their roles.
image_analysis.layout: The document has a header section with form information and the filer's name. The main body is structured in a list format, with each entry identified by a reference number. Each entry details an entity, its owners ('Owned by:'), their percentage ownership, name, and role. Some entries also list entities in which the primary entity has an ownership interest. A footer contains a document identifier.
